FBIS3-56426 "drsov011_b_94013" FBIS-SOV-94-011 Document Type:Daily Report 18 Jan 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Offered Finance Minister Role LD1701184894 Moscow INTERFAX in English 1807 GMT 17 Jan 94 LD1701184894 Moscow INTERFAX Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Meeting Boris Fedorov Monday night, Russia's Prime Minister Viktor Chernomyrdin offered him the post of finance minister "but not in the rank of deputy prime minister." As Fedorov told journalists in the Duma, he was given one and a half to two hours to think the proposal over and announce the final decision on whether he would stay in the cabinet.
